Value PORT (\S+)
Value NAME (.+?)
Value STATUS (connected|notconnect|disabled|up|down)
Value VLAN (\S+)
Value DUPLEX (\S+)
Value SPEED (\S+(?:\s+[GM]bps)?)
Value TYPE (\S+)

Start
  ^---- -> Interfaces

Interfaces
  ^${PORT}\s+${STATUS}\s+${VLAN}\s+${DUPLEX}\s+${SPEED}\s+${TYPE}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^${PORT}\s+${NAME}\s+${STATUS}\s+${VLAN}\s+${DUPLEX}\s+${SPEED}\s+${TYPE}\s*$$ -> Record
